Source: ubuntu-mate-colours
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Luke Horwell <luke@ubuntu-mate.org>
Standards-Version: 4.1.3
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11),
               python3 (>= 3.4.0),
               librsvg2-bin,
               imagemagick,
               libglib2.0-bin,
               libgtk-3-dev,
               meson,
               sassc,
               ubuntu-mate-icon-themes,
               ubuntu-mate-themes,
               ubuntu-mate-wallpapers-common
Homepage: https://github.com/lah7/ubuntu-mate-colours

Package: ubuntu-mate-colours-all
Architecture: all
Depends: ubuntu-mate-colours-aqua,
         ubuntu-mate-colours-blue,
         ubuntu-mate-colours-brown,
         ubuntu-mate-colours-orange,
         ubuntu-mate-colours-pink,
         ubuntu-mate-colours-purple,
         ubuntu-mate-colours-red,
         ubuntu-mate-colours-teal,
         ubuntu-mate-colours-yellow
Description: Complete collection of Ubuntu MATE variants
 Contains all the colour variants of:
 - Ambiant-MATE
 - Ambiant-MATE-Dark
 - Radiant-MATE
 - Yaru-MATE-Light
 - Yaru-MATE-Dark
 .
 This includes wallpapers, icons and themes.

Package: ubuntu-mate-colours-aqua
Architecture: all
Depends: gtk-update-icon-cache,
         ubuntu-mate-themes,
         ubuntu-mate-icon-themes,
         ubuntu-mate-wallpapers-common
Description: Aqua variant of Ubuntu MATE themes
 Contains aqua coloured versions of Ambiant-MATE, Ambiant-MATE-Dark,
 Radiant-MATE, Yaru-MATE-Light and Yaru-MATE-Dark.
 .
